    public enum AwsInjectableTag
extends java.lang.Enum<AwsInjectableTag>
implements com.netflix.servo.tag.Tag
    Group of Tags who's values will be dynamically set at runtime based on amazon api calls.

    The keys for and values of these Tags are consistent with AWS naming.
